or);\n    }\n  })", "is_member_call": false, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L198"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "includes", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L255"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "trim", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse\\src\\security-classifier.ts", "source_location": "L256"}, {"caller_nid": "src_security_classifier_htmltoplaintext", "callee": "replace", "is_member_call": true, "source_file": "C:\\business-pult\\gstack\\browse